				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Finally got my 4th rune and the new Bolt  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_dance.gif" alt="Dancing" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
I am currently spec'd Conjuration, I have the ornate gloves and use Sun Vortex mainly.  I use the summoned earring to save mana on Black Steel.
<br />

<br />
Is the new bolt and summoned earring going to be as efficient as Sun Vortex and ornate gloves if I switch specialization?  I seem to be the only mage left in my guild who is not spec evoc, and with bolts never missing anymore I am starting to wonder why.
<br />

<br />
My gear and AA are up to date in my sig (I think), any help on deciding this would be appreciated.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="text-decoration: underline"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=531028" target="_blank" class="postlink">Pharmer Enthedell</a></span></span> - Arch Convoker
