				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">More often that not at the higher end raids I'm seeing a lot more resists on BoJ than I am with Ancient:  Chaotic Vortex or Burning Earth.  I'm not sure why, but that seems to be the way it is (maybe I'm just unlucky).  There are a few raid mobs that get hit for full with BoJ 90% of the time-- Ture for example.  Other than that, I tend not to use BoJ on raids much.
<br />

