				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well after looking on Lucy for all the info I tried to crunch numbers between the BoJ and SV.  I tried to look at longer term as well as short term.  I did not count the specialization/SCM numbers.
<br />

<br />
Comparing semi equal mana useage for short fight,
<br />

<br />
BoJ,
<br />

<br />
10 casts@ 625mana (-15% MP) = 5312.5 mana,  27,510 dmg  in ~1min30sec
<br />

<br />
SV,
<br />

<br />
17 casts@ 390mana (-20% MP) = 5304 mana,  26,350 dmg but took ~2min12sec
<br />

<br />
The number of casts required would make quite a difference in zones where mounts are not allowed for me.
<br />

<br />
Long term numbers considering 100 casts of each really show the dps difference as well as mana difference.
<br />

<br />
BoJ,
<br />

<br />
100 casts@625mana(-15% MP)= 53,125 mana,  275,100 dmg and ~16min40sec
<br />

<br />
SV,
<br />

<br />
100 cast@390mana(-20% MP)= 31,200 mana,  155,000 dmg and takes ~15min
<br />

<br />
I tried to figure SV at arund 16min40sec of casting too, it was around,
<br />

<br />
111 casts@ 390mana(-20% MP)= 34,632 mana 172,050 dmg
<br />

<br />

<br />
I used to be spec evoc, I switched for black steel and sun vortex because back then the bolts actually had a chance of missing, and also because Pet Canni was a wonderful thing.  
<br />

<br />
I hve not gotten all the OoW spells, no where close to it, and my luck with rolls on runes is almost as bad as my getting groups where named spawn.
<br />

<br />
Guess I could just switch it and switch back if it does not seem better.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="text-decoration: underline"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=531028" target="_blank" class="postlink">Pharmer Enthedell</a></span></span> - Arch Convoker
