				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">One problem with your calcs.
<br />

<br />
Mana preservation is only 10%, and since BoJ is a 66 spell, your MP-4 downgrades 1 level, so it is really 9%.
<br />

<br />
10 casts@ 625mana (-9% MP) = 5687.5 mana for 27,510 dmg
<br />

<br />
Blade Strike
<br />

<br />
14 casts @ 443mana (-7% MP) = 5767 mana for  26,964 dmg
<br />

<br />
So these 2 nukes are very close, before you put specialization into the mix.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: normal">Lord Zacatac Soulwanderer</a></span></span></span>
