			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The focus effects go down by 10% per level of efficiency.
<br />

<br />
So ID-4 is 20% at 65
<br />
18% at 66
<br />
16% at 67
<br />
14% at 68
<br />
etc
<br />

<br />
So you would have to use Itchy's spreadsheet to see how it all balances out.
<br />

<br />
As for the magic focus, I use Glowing Stone of Expulsion, which is 25% to magic and therefore an equal match for the CRoB.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4796" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: normal">Lord Zacatac Soulwanderer</a></span></span></span>
